# Traffic Light Controller Using Logic Gates

## Overview

This project implements a traffic light controller using digital logic gates and a custom PCB.

The system was designed from logic-level operation instead of microcontroller programming, then fabricated into a real PCB and tested successfully.

## Features

* Traffic light sequence implemented with logic circuits
* Custom PCB design
* Physical hardware testing
* Schematic and PCB layout included

## Components

* Logic Gates (AND / OR / NOT / NAND / NOR)
* Timer / Counter IC (if used)
* LEDs
* Power Supply

## Design Flow

Truth Table → Logic Simplification → Schematic → PCB Design → Fabrication → Testing

